reviews.review_text:
Best of the AUD bunch? Except for the hiss, I think this AUD is the best of the bunch. Many thanks for the upload!
I saw DSO re-create this setlist at Salvage Station, their last scheduled concert at Salvage Station before it's supposed to be taken down. That was such a great venue too

Second set, while a little bog standard, is really good. Cassidy is best of first set (I also love the song). Worth the download!
